  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Career</h2>Race your way from stock Group D vehicles all the way up to pro rally Group R beasts. Choose your path through the career as you in 55 race series. Collect stars and liveries by winning races, collect vehicles by winning championships. The career will keep you in the driver seat for up to 11-25 hours.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Trials</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/f99d00be971df943d83823ad0e5aba3d.poster.avif?t=1672170803\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/f99d00be971df943d83823ad0e5aba3d.webm?t=1672170803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/f99d00be971df943d83823ad0e5aba3d.mp4?t=1672170803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Improve your skills and compete with other players to set your best pace on 672 world-wide leaderboards. Each of the 8 race courses has 12 track layouts with dynamic traction surfaces that will keep you on your toes lap after lap.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Racing</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/ab533b20e77f8a672041547d717c3c55.poster.avif?t=1672170803\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/ab533b20e77f8a672041547d717c3c55.webm?t=1672170803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/ab533b20e77f8a672041547d717c3c55.mp4?t=1672170803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Customize your online races with control over the laps, time, damage, and more. Create a quick 3 lap sprint or a grueling 24 hour endurance race, the options are endless. Multiplayer also has a Free Roam mode to explore each map with your friends. You choose how you want to play.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destruction</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/49b3004a8703758637aa2c95c553cbfc.poster.avif?t=1672170803\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/49b3004a8703758637aa2c95c553cbfc.webm?t=1672170803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/49b3004a8703758637aa2c95c553cbfc.mp4?t=1672170803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each of the 27 vehicles have their performance impacted as you make contact with other players, walls, and obstacles. From bent suspension and steering to losing wheels and tires, driving carelessly will keep you from the top of the podium.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free Roam</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/ed8201fa127d8fff3f73475f8d528f76.poster.avif?t=1672170803\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/ed8201fa127d8fff3f73475f8d528f76.webm?t=1672170803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/ed8201fa127d8fff3f73475f8d528f76.mp4?t=1672170803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take as much time as you need in a casual drive around the track. Try a new line through a corner or nail a specific braking zone. Add some friends in multiplayer and explore everything each course has to offer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394460/extras/300046e202c9de6b0844bedc454c25ed.avif?t=1672170803\" width=616 height=2718 /></span>",
